sentences: George Carroll, better known as Slaine, is an American rapper and actor.
Slaine has appeared on several solo mixtapes and compilations and on the Special Teamz album Stereotypez.
He is part of the  supergroup La Coka Nostra.
His debut solo album, A World With No Skies, saw release in August 2011, and he is also working on albums with both of his groups.
Slaine's acting career includes the films Gone Baby Gone (2007), The Town (2010), Killing Them Softly (2012), and Central Intelligence (2016).
He was also in the Netflix movie Wheelman (2017), and he played a character named Loverboy in the 2014 slasher film Girl House.
